<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_341_r1l23">Hilpolten <expan>frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_341_r1l24">Ein gelaubſbrief . auf Hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu reden von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_341_r1l25">hab vnd kaufmanſchaft wegen . als Hılpolt <expan>frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_341_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf dem Nortgaw aufgehalten vnd gen Prunn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_341_r1l27">gefurt hat . etc vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> . / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_341" id="170r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hilpolten <expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ein gelaubsbrief auf Hansen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> czu reden von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und kaufmanschaft wegen, als Hilpolt
                                <expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf dem Nortgaw aufgehalten und gen Prunn
                        gefurt hat etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
